Package edu.bpl.pwsplugin.acquisitionsequencer.steps

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Step.SimFn
    Recieves a SimulatedStatus and returns the same object.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BrokenStep
    Used as a placeholder in the event that a step fails to load from file successfully.
    ContainerStep<T extends JsonableParam>
    A `Step` that takes other `Step`s and wraps functionality around them.
    EndpointStep<T extends JsonableParam>
    A `Step` which is an endpoint (does not support containing any substeps
    EnterSubfolderStep
    Tells the sequencer to create and work within a new subfolder.
    IteratingContainerStep<T extends JsonableParam>
    A base class for ContainerSteps that run their child steps multiple times.
    RootStep
    Represents the mandatory initial step of the experiment.
    Step<T extends JsonableParam>
    Base class for a single step in the acquisition sequencer.
    Step.SimulatedStatus
    A single instance of this class is passed between the simulation functions to keep track of multiple parameters.
